{"tid":603242,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以用USB行Linux做Host OS，再用VM行Hackintosh + Windows","createTime":"2018-03-23T14:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T23:02:16.000Z","uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a9b2e7a4139640bb8ea2c6ce8688b156caa707","tid":603242,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"我而家係一隻SSD Dual Boot Hackintosh + Windows 10<br />\n但係換OS要重新開機其實都有啲麻煩，而且有時都想兩邊同時用<br />\n<br />\nCPU : i7-4790K<br />\nMB : Asrock Z97 Extreme 3<br />\n<br />\n想盡量唔改動現有嘅軟/硬件<br />\n有冇可能就咁加隻USB落去行Linux<br />\n跟住直接用VM Run返現有嘅macOS同Windows？<br />\n<br />\nWindows嗰邊需要GPU Passthrough<br />\nHackintosh都可能要，有需要嘅話我可以加張舊顯示咭<br />\n<br />\n有冇例子可以參考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1eb9ef8334dfdb39476dc592178fff1feedf44","tid":603242,"uid":89015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"你自己答咗自己了: P2V using VMware"},{"pid":"0ce9e9298d549796d77c520ededf82f219da7f8f","tid":603242,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"7f97cc615678417b8ff83da9a40df60f29b29002","tid":603242,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce9e9298d549796d77c520ededf82f219da7f8f","tid":603242,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"個例子係你？"},{"pid":"1234d35cafad087ce8879c17c81346e3f3b50ecf","tid":603242,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f97cc615678417b8ff83da9a40df60f29b29002","tid":603242,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce9e9298d549796d77c520ededf82f219da7f8f","tid":603242,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"個例子係你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime