macOS<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔及Linux可靠<br />\n同埋主要想同時Run兩個OS<br />\n所以先有咁嘅打算<br />\n而且效能唔係優先考慮因素，最緊要Work到先<br />\n<br />\n未試過直接喺USB行，想知點解唔可行？"},{"pid":"cff541b5f0efdaf94a9d75f3d50e5b6a0e264587","tid":603242,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:02:16.000Z","msg":"a 狗剩係係非linux post 吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}